body:
## What happened

Just launched the IDE and it reported an error during startup. All other functions of the IDE seem to work. I only started seeing this error after the last flutter plugin update. I am not sure if this needed to be reported so delete if it is not helpful. 

## Version information

Android Studio `Bumblebee | 2021.1.1 Patch 2` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 65.0.2` • Dart plugin `211.7798`

Error getting Flutter sdk information.

[✓] Android Studio (version 2021.1)
[✓] Connected device (4 available)

• No issues found!
